      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_4D9723C0-2220-0135-2C25-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the name of the graded discussion</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_rubric" data-step-uuid="E394C98D-2C13-4A1D-985E-25F16C76480A">
    <h2 id="add_rubric" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Rubric</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/251/167/original/d11a0852-7dba-411e-aa5a-c7e0d0eee0cd.png" srcset="" alt="Add Rubric" height="286" width="829">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_4D975590-2220-0135-2C27-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1] and select the <strong>Add Rubric</strong> option [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="add-rubric-in-discussions-redesign" data-step-uuid="8f833d40-d701-4e52-9a2f-928a0ac670ac">
    <h3 id="add-rubric-in-discussions-redesign" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Rubric in Discussions Redesign</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/681/054/original/a5fc92ee-b8a3-4f57-b0a3-2ec87ecb590d.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/681/054/medium/a5fc92ee-b8a3-4f57-b0a3-2ec87ecb590d.png" srcset="" alt="Add Rubric in Discussions Redesign" height="421" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_f49d4150-f1b7-4438-8a88-ffaf1fedc9e0" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To add a rubric in Discussions Redesign, click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1] and select the <strong>Add Rubric</strong> link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-assignment-rubric-details" data-step-uuid="97dbf580-cc82-4dad-8c7b-6b1e6ee902d6">
    <h2 id="view-assignment-rubric-details" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Assignment Rubric Details</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/681/056/original/1219faff-b9fa-4217-aecc-ebb7003edb9b.png" srcset="" alt="View Assignment Rubric Details" height="139" width="632">
